  "source": "Taittiriya Upanishad — Peace Invocation",
  "sanskrit": "ॐ सह नाववतु\nसह नौ भुनक्तु\nसह वीर्यं करवावहै\nतेजस्वि नावधीतमस्तु\nमा विद्विषावहै\nॐ शान्तिः शान्तिः शान्तिः",
  "meaning": "May we be protected together. May we be nourished together. May we work with great energy together. May our study be brilliant. May we not dispute with each other. Om — peace, peace, peace.",
